{"tid":1881493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港最多保護衣o既正菩部門唔係衛生署同消防，係狗賊","createTime":"2020-02-15T14:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T04:41:56.000Z","uid":51271,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d8785ebd0d5ce7709dbe84889a664058f4964ff2","tid":1881493,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"武漢新型冠狀病毒疫情持續，全港抗疫物資不足。根據蘋果日報取得的文件顯示，政府首輪分配的抗疫物資中，警察獲發約 64 萬個口罩，是獲發口罩第二多的政府部門，食環署僅及警方一半。而警方獲發的 N95 口罩更多達 1.3 萬個，衛生署只獲發不足 300 個。同時，警方更預計 2 月至 4 月需要逾 4 萬件全身防護衣，但衛生署只需要逾 2000 件全身防護衣。<br />\n<br />\n根據蘋果日報報道，取得的文件顯示政府在首輪分配抗疫物資中，衛生署獲發 130 萬個口罩，警務處則排第二，獲發約 64 萬個口罩，食環署僅及警方一半。N95口罩方面，警方獲發達 1.3 萬個，是各部門之冠，衛生署都只獲發不足 300 個。<br />\n<br />\n政府各部門亦有提交預期的數量，警方則預期 2 月至 4 月需要 2 萬 6000 件保護袍（Gown）、逾4萬件全身防護衣（Protective Coverall Suit），衛生署需要 7 萬件保護袍及逾 2000 件全身防護衣.<br />\n<br />\n報道指，分配口罩由政府物流署中央負責，最優先供應衛生署，如果食衛局認為有必須分配予醫管局，醫管局亦是最優先級別。其次優先是一些提供緊急服務部門、基本公共服務，特別是紀律部隊和一些前線人員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/items-21_J10ne_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fitems-21_J10ne_1200x0.png&h=07496afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C-%E8%AD%A6%E7%8D%B2%E7%99%BC-64-%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E5%90%84%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%9A-n95-1-3-%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B-%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3-300%E5%80%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%2599%25BC-64-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E5%2590%2584%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%25A4%259A-n95-1-3-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258B-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3-300%25E5%2580%258B%2F&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=523cb6e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%2599%25BC-64-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E5%2590%2584%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%25A4%259A-n95-1-3-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258B-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3-300%25E5%2580%258B%2F&h=3990268f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C-%E8%AD%A6%E7%8D%B2%E7%99%BC-64-%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E5%90%84%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%9A-n95-1-3-%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B-%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3-300%E5%80%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"4ba3ccd898ab1afcd650dc7200ed7a0b21c30389","tid":1881493,"uid":189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"好似未見過黑警以外嘅部門著黑警嗰款保護衣，救護衞生署都係著啲薄到透嗰隻"},{"pid":"ecbda697e564ab1613ff673f88eb9cb821e15251","tid":1881493,"uid":169048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:52:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑狗"},{"pid":"6b097d8ff29f7fa4d0249ac0077b700279ab5d72","tid":1881493,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"b4fdb7c3c6ffddc2643788db4995a00657bcc95d","tid":1881493,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"7.21"},{"pid":"e60dffde421109a2046ac929ff08b84eef873a7b","tid":1881493,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:35:54.000Z","msg":"警方30000人<br />\n就算有一半唔上前線<br />\n都15000人<br />\n衛生署成個編制得7000人<br />\n仲包埋牙醫嗰D唔駛做檢疫既人落去<br />\n有得咁比??"},{"pid":"fac4f68a68f